projects.Title: HIGH PERFORMANCE HARDWARE IMPLEMENTATION OF AES USING MINIMAL RESOURCES
projects.Description: The Hardware Implementation of AES Using Minimal Resources in order to achieve higher speed and lesser area. The algorithms used in AES are so simple that they can be easily implemented using cheap processors and a minimum amount of memory with low RAM requirements which gives high security assurance and efficiency.
